'''"Threading the needle"''' was an infamous move among the [[Swoop/Legends|swoop]] and [[T-16 skyhopper|skyhopper]] racers of [[Beggar's Canyon/Legends|Beggar's Canyon]] in which they would successfully jump through the [[Stone Needle/Legends|Stone Needle]]. A slight miscalculation in this move would cause certain death. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] was one of very few who threaded the needle and survived.<ref name="A Wind">{{SWRadio|A Wind to Shake the Stars}}</ref>

